    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 58-61.</p><p>Slayer of Legends</p><p>Starting at 25th level, you have become the ultimate slayer, capable of taking down even the most storied foes. When you hit a creature marked by your Slayer’s Mark with a critical hit, you regain 1 Legendary Point. Once you regain a Legendary Point in this way, you cannot do so again until the end of your next turn.</p><p>5e. In addition, creatures of CR 20 or higher, or any character of 20th level or higher, count as Favored Enemies for you, even if they are of a creature type you have not chosen as your Favored Enemy.</p></div>",
